Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being late for our weekly get-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will NOT BELIEVE what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's much more than all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way here,\Nwearing my latest hat creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...when who should stop me on the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But Photo Finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the most famous fashion\Nphotographer in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywho, she saw my hat and said\Nit was absolutely marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She was so impressed that she wants\Nto take some pictures of my shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...featuring some of my clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this could\Nmean for my fashion career?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity, I'm so happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to need somepony\Nfabulous to model for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony with beauty.\NSomepony with grace. Somepony...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is such a huge opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would mean so much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony is going to have\Nyour elegance and poise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-Nopony!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-There has to be somepony more quali...\N-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Somepony more into fashion.\N-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Somepony more comfortable in the spotlight\N-Please, please, PLEEEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it's that important to you,\Nof course I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thankyouthankyouthankyouthankyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the best friend a pony could ever have!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful way to spend an afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I was so afraid you wouldn't agree\Nto model for me that I felt completely frazzled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I feel a pimple coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Only one solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... She's going to want to\Nsee attitude and pizzazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a-attitude and, um... pizzazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,More light! It has to catch\Nthe sequins just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...or the whole outfit is just a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the headdress need more feathers.\NPinkie Pie! More feathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And sequins! More sequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And more ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Less ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No! More ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this hem is completely off.\NPINCUSHION!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to be so short with you,\Nbut I'm... I'm just so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, doesn't that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thick scales. Can't feel a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is no pain that would\Nkeep me from assisting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...the most beautiful creature in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell you two a secret.\NBut you have to promise not to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross my heart and hope to fly,\NStick a cupcake in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a crush on Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't say a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. Everypony\Nalready knows how you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! You promised Spike\Nyou wouldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He trusts you. And losing a friend's trust\Nis the fastest way to lose a friend forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My lips are sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm pretty sure Rarity is\Ngonna pick up on your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Photo Finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...have awwived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitude and pizzazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Show Photo Finish something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She hardly took any pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I tried my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the headdress is too big for you\Nand cape had too much sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I ever thought\N*I* could impress *her*.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I, Photo Finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...have found a next fashion star\Nhere in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, Photo Finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...am going to help her\Nto shine all over Eqvestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow a photo shoot in ze park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to "shine all over Equestria".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity. I was so worried\NI'd ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never. I knew you'd be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is definitely the one.\NPhoto Finish is going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony is going to love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am so excited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget us little ponies when you become\Nthe most famous designer in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nonononononono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The model should be in something simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something inspired by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...the nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... give me a moment and I'll, uh,\Nput a little something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... that will not be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but... how are you going to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,..."shine across Equestria"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I don't design something\Nnew for these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not going to help you\Nshine across Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to help *her* shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you must, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish wants to make you a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the opportunity of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we were both hoping\Nit would be my lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...but nonetheless you can't\Nthrow away this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You must. You must! YOU MUST!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Floottershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...the magics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wunderbar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are like a delicate flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So much more alluring without\Nall those sparkles und feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it go? How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish wanted to work\Nwith Fluttershy, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just vant to be alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her. She vants to be... alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't think she meant *alone* alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enuf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enuf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfiect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Even her schneezes are gressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,NOW GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel? Excited? Overjoyed?\NFrilled beyond your wildest dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,N... nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nervous? Dun be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only facing a large crowd of ponies...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...who will be watching your every move\Nand silently judging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cue! Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't let Rarity down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do this. You must. You must. You must.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-So graceful.\N-So lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So perfect for my new advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Look how popular you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be having the best time ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Best time ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Flootershy! I have been\Nlooking for you everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the thing at the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you at the spa. Our usual time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I can't wait to hear all about the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,..."thing" at the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be\Nmobbed by strangers wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Carousel Boutique!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she still here? We heard Fluttershy was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You just missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still in luck. I'm having\Na huge sale of some of my best designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Never heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously I, Photo Finish,\Nam fwilled to have found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-She's a natural in front of the camera.\N-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I only need to point\Nand shoot and I capture...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...the magics!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish, I'm so sorry to interrupt.\NIt's just that I'm running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your appearance at the ballet opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony who is anypony will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually I'm supposed\Nto be meeting my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My hooves are getting positively pruney,\NI've been waiting here so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously Fluttershy's just too busy with her\Nnew *career* to spend time with her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she just got tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she did.\NShe's a big bright shining star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish that star would burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Fluttershy is your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I should be happy for her, but instead I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please promise you won't\Ntell her I feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please, pleasepleasePLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing a friend's trust is\Nthe fastest way to lose a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy may be the one who's famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that doesn't mean\NI have to stop looking fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! I'm so sorry I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. She's already gone, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so frustrated I could just scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can I tell you something?\N-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise not to tell Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie-swear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross my heart and hope to fly,\NStick a cupcake in my AARGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I hate being a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All this attention is awful, just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm only doing it because Rarity\Ntold me I must. I must! I MUST!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know the truth, Rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what were you about to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really don't like being a model,\Nyou could always quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I could never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity would be devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rarity told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... Juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if only all these ponies\Ndidn't like me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Photo Finish wouldn't want me to model anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd find somepony else with...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...the magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, you're fight, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see? On her own, Fluttershy\Ncould never do something unattractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I used my magic to help her do something\Nunattractive on her next fashion show...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...no one would ever want her to model again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Fluttershy no longer has to be a model,\NRarity will no longer have to be jealous of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll no longer have to keep their secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell anyone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you won't tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-s-so you do promise or you don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, that's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zipped my mouth closed, then locked it with a key...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...then dug a hole, then buried the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...then built a house up top the hole\Nwhere I buried the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...then moved into the house atop the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They love you for being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So all I have to do is make you *not* be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's time to see what all the fuss is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her off the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an embarrassment to all things fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Photo Finish, have made a terrible mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I say bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo? Who could possibly say\Nbravo to that horrid display?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Such attitude! Such pizzazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's invented an entirely\Nnew kind of modeling! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is saying these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The unicorn in the gorgeous cape and headdress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that is a pony, who clearly\Nknows a thing or two about fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that fabulous pony likes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I do too! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful. Just awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I've become more popular than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so frustrated I could just kick something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Rarity didn't want me to be a model so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rarity...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm great! I'm a super famous fashion model.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I be great?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you ha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Out there on the runway,\Neveryone was turning on you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... oh, Fluttershy. It's so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she did! Because...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted all the attention.\NAnd instead it was going to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I even started hoping that you would do something\Nsilly so your modeling career would be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, when it started happening,\Nall I could think was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...how could I want you to fail\Nat something you love so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Fluttershy doesn't... Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Love? Oh, Rarity. I hate being a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you keep doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid if I quit, you'd be\Nmad at me for not wanting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,..."shine all over Equestria".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought if I told you how jealous I was\Nof your success, you'd think I was a terrible friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just told each other the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise never to keep my feelings in secret again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross my heart and hope to fly,\NStick a cupcake in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were brilliant. Brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got six photo shoots\Nlined up for tomorrow aloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Photo Finish, but I don't think\NI'll be able to make any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vat has just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike has a crush on Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is a wonderful way\Nto spend an afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Being a good friend means\Nbeing able to keep a secret."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"But you should never be afraid to\Nshare your true feelings with a good friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get all that, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe you told someone\Nabout my secret feelings for Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. That was\Nwrong of me and I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Apology accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now will you take down\Nmy letter to Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm a little busy at the moment.
